						<summary>

						<p>On a rock near the Varadarāja-perumāḷ temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara: Śrīraṅgarāyadēva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1568, Vyaya, Mārgaśira śu. 5, corresponding to 1647 A.D., January 5, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of land by Daḷavāyi Apā-Nāyini, the agent of the king.</p>						

						</summary>
